text: Novonikolsk () is large village in the Ussuriysky Urban Okrug of Primorsky Krai of Russia. Novonikolsk is the center of a rural area which includes the villages of Elitnoe and Stepnoe. Founded in 1866, but the official founding date of 1910 is considered. Village Council == References == Category:Rural localities in Primorsky Krai
title: Novonikolsk, Primorsky Krai
